column5: I made it out the other day to try and best my wife's fish from a couple weeks past...I wasn't able to beat hers but I did get a new PB, a 30"x20".  A better story to follow on my blog later tonight when I have a bit more time.
Nice looking fish! Judging by the calm waters, they're all jiggin fish?
Very nice lakers.Congrats   I would bet with those depths,there,s got to be a monster in that lake.
congrats on your PB. couple of beauty fish there
all on downriggers and a spoon
